            <Comment>
                potential special cases:
                - Terran building burning down (unit: SupplyDepot, player 1, killer 1, deathType normal, effect BurndownDamage, damagePos 33,45)
                - unit dies within shot down transport: unit: SCV, player 1, killer 16, deathType INHERITED, effect , damagePos 0,0
