                - Adept Phase shifting (unit AdeptPhaseShift, player 1, killer 1, deathType normal, effect AdeptPhaseShiftKillDummy, damagePos 31.9795,37.7231)
                - Adept Phase shifting Cancel (unit AdeptPhaseShift, player 1, killer 1, deathType normal, effect AdeptPhaseShiftKillDummy, damagePos 19.0935,37.0576)
